
dmidecode : -s <string_keyword> ( can be found also on /sys/class/dmi/id )
            -t <type_number/keywork>
dmesg     : -T  = display timestamp into a human-friendly format
lspci     : -vv = more infos
lsusb     : -vv = morfe info

Note: for CPU,Memory and Disk hardware refer to each of the files

